<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="About_intellectual_history">About intellectual history</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Intellectual_history&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: About intellectual history"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
